Air More Uptempo 'White Varsity Red' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air More Uptempo ‘White Varsity Red’ brings back a simple two-tone colorway also known as the ‘Renowned Rhythm,’ a reference to the dynamic playing style of Chicago Bulls forward Scottie Pippen. Originally released in the mid-2000s and previously reissued in 2018, the mid-top sports a pristine white leather upper, accented with oversized ‘AIR’ lettering outlined in red. A matching crimson jewel Swoosh adorns the back heel. Three distinct Nike Air units are housed in a lightweight Phylon midsole, supported underfoot by a herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Superstar Primeblue Chalk White
results.story: The adidas Superstar Primeblue ‘White Black’ updates the iconic silhouette with refreshed detailing and a sustainable build. Primeblue branding is displayed on the lateral side, indicating that the white textile upper incorporates upcycled Parley Ocean Plastic, highlighted by a black netting-like overlay that wraps around the heel. Semi-translucent rubber is utilized on the sneaker’s shell toe and durable cupsole, the latter featuring a traditional herringbone tread underfoot.

results.name: Reebok Answer IV OG 20th Anniversary
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Reebok Answer 4 OG ‘White Red’ brings back Allen Iverson’s signature shoe from the 2000 – 2001 season, which culminated with AI’s lone MVP nod and his only trip to the Finals. The sleek silhouette features a white leather upper with a contrasting red leather toe wrap. ‘I3’ branding adorns synthetic forefoot inserts, coated in a reflective grey finish for enhanced visibility. An added Velcro strap wraps over a zippered shroud that conceals the lace bed. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a DMX foam midsole, supported by a rubber outsole that features AI’s likeness and an engraved ‘Only the Strong Survive’ tagline.

Clyde All-Pro 'Coast 2 Coast - Celtics'
results.story: Launching alongside a Los Angeles Lakers-inspired colorway, the PUMA Clyde All-Pro Coast 2 Coast ‘Celtics’ celebrates an iconic NBA rivalry that has yielded the most Finals matchups in league history. This pair gives the nod to Boston, featuring a white Matryx knit upper with green accents and a black leather Formstrip on the lateral side. The low-top rides on a full-length ProFoam+ midsole made with high-rebound EVA. Underfoot, a grippy rubber outsole reveals a Pebax drop in the heel.

Puma Clyde All-Pro Low Lakers
results.story: The PUMA Clyde All-Pro Coast 2 Coast ‘Lakers’ draws inspiration from an iconic NBA rivalry that dates back to 1959. Launching alongside an accompanying Boston Celtics colorway, this pair reps Los Angeles with contrasting purple and gold accents on a Matryx engineered knit upper. Performance benefits include a Pebax puck under the heel, a propulsion plate in the forefoot and a full-length ProFoam+ midsole for lightweight and responsive cushioning.

KD 14 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike KD 14 ‘Black White’ represents the debut colorway of Kevin Durant’s 14th signature shoe, which brings back the midfoot strap last seen on the KD 7. Textile overlays create an intricate all-over print throughout the minimalist upper, reinforced with molded mesh construction at the heel. Nods to Nike heritage include an elongated Swoosh that recalls the Bruin, while the medial side of the midfoot strap is redolent of the Presto. The lightweight build sits atop a Cushlon foam midsole, supplemented by a full-length Air Zoom Strobel.

Air Max 90 Golf 'Aurora Hot Punch'
results.story: Built for the links, the Nike Air Max 90 Golf ‘Aurora Hot Punch’ stays true to its ‘90s running roots with retro cushioning and vibrant accents. The white mesh upper is reinforced with a water-resistant coating and fused synthetic overlays in grey and black. A pink cropped Swoosh adorns the side panel, while cassette detailing in an aqua hue frames the Max Air unit in the heel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features an integrated traction pattern made to grip the turf during rotational movements.

results.name: Parley x Terrex Free Hiker 'Aluminium Sesame'
results.story: The Parley x adidas Terrex Free Hiker ‘Aluminium Sesame’ applies a neutral monochromatic finish to an outdoor silhouette build in part with upcycled Parley Ocean Plastic, recovered from beaches and coastal communities before it floats out into the ocean. The sock-like upper is constructed from coated Primeknit textile with tonal no-sew overlays and a molded TPU heel counter. A stacked full-length Boost midsole is supported by an EVA stabilization frame and reinforced underfoot by a lugged Continental rubber outsole.

results.story: The Sneakersnstuff x New Balance 770 Made in England ‘Secret Flimby Experiment’ updates the retro ‘80s running shoe with a unique patchwork-like design. The low-top carries a black leather upper with printed pigskin suede overlays taken from an unusual source: leftover scraps from three different 1500 models, gathered from the floor of New Balance’s Flimby production facility. The sneaker rides on a lightweight ENCAP midsole, supported underfoot by a high-traction black rubber outsole.

Parley x Terrex Free Hiker 'Earth Trace Cargo'
results.story: The Parley x adidas Terrex Free Hiker ‘Earth Trace Cargo’ showcases a military-inspired palette on a rugged outdoor silhouette constructed with sustainability in mind. Upcycled Parley Ocean Plastic is incorporated into the charcoal-colored Primeknit upper, equipped with an elastic cuff and fortified with synthetic no-sew overlays. Responsive cushioning is provided by a khaki-hued Boost midsole, reinforced with an EVA stabilization frame for lateral support. Underfoot, a lugged Continental rubber outsole provides enhanced traction.

Parley x Terrex Free Hiker 'Black'
results.story: The Parley x adidas Terrex Free Hiker ‘Black’ delivers a stealthy edition of a lightweight trail shoe stripped of all color. Made in part with upcycled Parley Ocean Plastic, the sneaker-boot hybrid carries a breathable Primeknit upper equipped with an elastic cuff and a webbing pull loop at the heel. The mid-top is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole in a matching black finish. Underfoot, the Adaptive Traxion outsole features Continental rubber for grippy traction on uneven terrain.

results.name: Puma Court Rider White Multi
results.story: The PUMA Court Rider ‘Twofold’ highlights vibrant colors on a performance basketball shoe inspired by the brand’s Rider franchise. The lightweight textile upper is fortified with synthetic overlays and equipped with a breathable mesh tongue. A dynamic lacing system extends to the forefoot for a lockdown fit. High-rebound cushioning is provided by a full-length Rider foam midsole, accented with PUMA Formstrip branding and reinforced by a high-abrasion rubber outsole.
